  <description>
    <p>
      Goodvibes is a simple internet radio player for GNU/Linux.
    </p>
    <p>
      It comes with every basic features you can expect from an audio player,
      such as multimedia keys, notifications, system sleep inhibition, and
      MPRIS2 support.
    </p>
  </description>

